description: Lists of information about the signals (nodes) specified in a signal catalog.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the signal catalog to list information about.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: A pagination token for the next set of results. If the results of a search are large, only a portion of the results are returned, and a nextToken pagination token is returned in the response. To retrieve the next set of results, reissue the search request and include the returned token. When all results have been returned, the response does not contain a pagination token value.

nested_items.name: nodes
nested_items.description: A list of information about nodes.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the branch. For example, the fully qualified name of a branch might be Vehicle.Body.Engine.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the branch.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the sensor. For example, the fully qualified name of a sensor might be Vehicle.Body.Engine.Battery.

nested_items.name: dataType
nested_items.description: The specified data type of the sensor.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of a sensor.

nested_items.name: unit
nested_items.description: The scientific unit of measurement for data collected by the sensor.

nested_items.name: allowedValues
nested_items.description: A list of possible values a sensor can take.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: min
nested_items.description: The specified possible minimum value of the sensor.

nested_items.name: max
nested_items.description: The specified possible maximum value of the sensor.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: structFullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the struct node for a sensor if the data type of the actuator is Struct or StructArray. For example, the struct fully qualified name of a sensor might be Vehicle.ADAS.CameraStruct.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the actuator. For example, the fully qualified name of an actuator might be Vehicle.Front.Left.Door.Lock.

nested_items.name: dataType
nested_items.description: The specified data type of the actuator.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the actuator.

nested_items.name: unit
nested_items.description: The scientific unit for the actuator.

nested_items.name: allowedValues
nested_items.description: A list of possible values an actuator can take.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: min
nested_items.description: The specified possible minimum value of an actuator.

nested_items.name: max
nested_items.description: The specified possible maximum value of an actuator.

nested_items.name: assignedValue
nested_items.description: A specified value for the actuator.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: structFullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the struct node for the actuator if the data type of the actuator is Struct or StructArray. For example, the struct fully qualified name of an actuator might be Vehicle.Door.LockStruct.

nested_items.name: attribute
nested_items.description: Information about a node specified as an attribute.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the attribute. For example, the fully qualified name of an attribute might be Vehicle.Body.Engine.Type.

nested_items.name: dataType
nested_items.description: The specified data type of the attribute.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the attribute.

nested_items.name: unit
nested_items.description: The scientific unit for the attribute.

nested_items.name: allowedValues
nested_items.description: A list of possible values an attribute can be assigned.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: min
nested_items.description: The specified possible minimum value of the attribute.

nested_items.name: max
nested_items.description: The specified possible maximum value of the attribute.

nested_items.name: assignedValue
nested_items.description: A specified value for the attribute.

nested_items.name: defaultValue
nested_items.description: The default value of the attribute.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the custom structure. For example, the fully qualified name of a custom structure might be ComplexDataTypes.VehicleDataTypes.SVMCamera.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the custom structure.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: fullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the custom property. For example, the fully qualified name of a custom property might be ComplexDataTypes.VehicleDataTypes.SVMCamera.FPS.

nested_items.name: dataType
nested_items.description: The data type for the custom property.

nested_items.name: dataEncoding
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the property is binary data.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the custom property.

nested_items.name: deprecationMessage
nested_items.description: The deprecation message for the node or the branch that was moved or deleted.

nested_items.name: comment
nested_items.description: A comment in addition to the description.

nested_items.name: structFullyQualifiedName
nested_items.description: The fully qualified name of the struct node for the custom property if the data type of the custom property is Struct or StructArray.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to retrieve the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
